<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TT2.5">
<l>muḷḷi tīntu muḷari karuki mūḷai corintukkuk</l>
<l>kaḷḷi vaṟṟi veḷḷil piṟaṅku kaṭuveṅ kāṭṭuḷḷē</l>
<l>puḷḷi yuḻaimāṉ ṟōloṉ ṟuṭuttup pulittōl piyaṟkiṭṭup</l>
<l>paḷḷi yiṭamu matuvē yākap parama ṉāṭumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>On the harsh hot cremation ground, where thorny bushes are burnt, thorny twigs</l>
<l>blackened, brain is spilt [and] trickles, Euphorbia is withered, woodapple are large,</l>
<l>garbed in the skin of a spotted male antilope, putting the tiger skin to [his] neck</l>
<l>since that is [his] resting place the Highest one is dancing.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
